{"tid":2186032,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"牛市之二十年前曾經有個咗樣既傳說⋯","createTime":"2020-09-02T15:52:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T00:55:06.000Z","uid":40478,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cf04a0d6bff709c1b320475aff870f1aa7988683","tid":2186032,"uid":40478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T15:52:05.000Z","msg":"話說係二十年前，有個傳說話互聯網會改變世界<br />\n當時既intc被炒到上6、70蚊<br />\n後來既事大家都知道，互聯網真係改變左世界<br />\n而大眾當年對intc既想象亦都全部成真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結果係20年後既今日，intc真係值幾十蚊<br />\n當年高位all in intc既投資者，計埋息，應該終於回左本了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二十年後，新既傳說話tsla會改變世界<br />\n我都相信呢個係會成真既<br />\n但呢件事同閣下高位買左tsla會唔會發達，係兩回事黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e726ef0daac8196126e3464dd84a7e4403b0ee8b","tid":2186032,"uid":117648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T16:36:04.000Z","msg":"善心打破零回覆"},{"pid":"8f0d3541a711cbbd088b566158ac2fbe56f202d6","tid":2186032,"uid":352160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T16:36:12.000Z","msg":"因為INTC同internet完全冇關係<br />\n當年高位入msft一早發撚左達<p class=\"right\"></p>"},{"pid":"c1243a5aed48771e9824a9fd7dde7f7661d74e0a","tid":2186032,"uid":40478,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"8f0d3541a711cbbd088b566158ac2fbe56f202d6","tid":2186032,"uid":352160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T16:36:12.000Z","msg":"因為INTC同internet完全冇關係<br />\n當年高位入msft一早發撚左達<p class=\"right\"></p>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T16:41:19.000Z","msg":"Msft用左15年番到2000年高位<br />\n近5年升係靠cloud <br />\n最好2000年買入既人諗到十幾年後有cloud呢樣野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196b09010e649c1c3a601fdba5738267e0739e8d","tid":2186032,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T16:47:29.000Z","msg":"Intc兩里息"},{"pid":"eafa419fcd0e1fa7c3d57487a53cb325825